---
description: Adding New Features Checklist
globs: 
alwaysApply: false
---
1. Follow established patterns in similar modules
2. Add comprehensive type hints
3. Include proper error handling
4. Add comments for complex logic
5. Write docstrings with examples
6. Add and PASS tests covering all new functionality (unit and integration)
7. Update relevant __init__.py exports
8. Consider backward compatibility
9. Ensure code is production-ready (no placeholders or estimations)
10. Run the full test & lint suite (`uv run pytest`, `uv run ruff check`) and ensure **zero** failures before submission
